  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Girl-Friendly Latrine to Boost School Attendance</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Overriding goal of the project is to ensure Girls from 5 schools in Soroti District, Uganda will not have to miss school simply because they are menstruating. The project aims to install sanitary facilities by construction of 5 VIP Latrines, each with a water tank (rain harvest), well-furnished changing room for girls, and provision of hand washing facilities to support vulnerable girls. With your donation, we will enable girls to manage their periods and improve girl&apos;s education.</narrative>
  </description>
